# Widget sync + minify + dist

Standalone scripts (`aftercare-text-widget.js`, `aftercare-badge-poll.js`) live at the shadow-app repo root.

**After ANY edit to these files**, from `aftercare-abt-shadow-app/` you MUST run:

```bash
npm run build
```

This runs `sync-widget` (copy to `public/`, minify) and then Vite copies everything into `dist/`.

**Do not stop at `npm run sync-widget` alone** — `dist/` is what gets deployed and must always be updated with the change.

Do not run terser by hand unless debugging.
